<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>战区</title><link>https://www.twz.com</link><description>防御世界的强大进攻。</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 02 Jun 2026 03:57:57 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>俄罗斯卡车涂上“炫目”油漆以摆脱人工智能无人机</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/russian-trucks-get-dazzle-paint-to-throw-off-ai-enabled-drones</link><description>&lt;p&gt;随着自主无人机成为日益严重的威胁，这种颠覆性的涂料似乎旨在迷惑机器视觉瞄准系统。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/russian-trucks-get-dazzle-paint-to-throw-off-ai-enabled-drones"&gt;俄罗斯卡车获得“炫目”油漆以摆脱人工智能无人机的&lt;/a&gt;帖子首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jun 2026 23:41:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/russian-trucks-get-dazzle-paint-to-throw-off-ai-enabled-drones</guid></item><item><title>美国又飞MQ-1“捕食者”无人机了吗？</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/is-the-u-s-flying-mq-1-predator-drones-again</link><description>&lt;p&gt;围绕伊朗损失一架“MQ-1”的问题突显了将“捕食者”重新投入战斗的可能性和陷阱。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;帖子&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/is-the-u-s-flying-mq-1-predator-drones-again"&gt;美国又飞 MQ-1 捕食者无人机了吗？&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jun 2026 22:19:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/is-the-u-s-flying-mq-1-predator-drones-again</guid></item><item><title>针锋相对的袭击后，美伊停火濒临停火（更新）</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/u-s-iran-ceasefire-on-the-brink-after-tit-for-tat-attacks</link><description>&lt;p&gt;伊朗再次威胁要关闭曼德海峡，这进一步加剧了压力，该海峡现在是石油出口的绝对重要通道。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/u-s-iran-ceasefire-on-the-brink-after-tit-for-tat-attacks"&gt;针锋相对的袭击后，美伊停火濒临停火（更新）&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;“战区”&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jun 2026 22:03:08 