26 17:24:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/russian-drone-impacts-apartment-building-in-nato-state-romania-injuring-civilians</guid></item><item><title>国会推动海军无人机打击 HELIOS 激光器的集装箱变体</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/containerized-variant-of-navys-drone-swatting-helios-laser-being-pushed-by-congress</link><description>&lt;p&gt;HELIOS 是唯一能够击落安装在现役海军军舰上的无人机的激光器，将其放入集装箱中将开辟新的部署可能性。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/containerized-variant-of-navys-drone-swatting-helios-laser-being-pushed-by-congress"&gt;国会推动的海军无人机打击赫利俄斯激光的后集装箱变体&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 May 2026 16:58:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/containerized-variant-of-navys-drone-swatting-helios-laser-being-pushed-by-congress</guid></item></channel></rss>